| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5789 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 760d2aaa-43ec-51e8-a70b-1734b44cf1ad"
